GynoSMART services can be accessed both online and offline 

**1. Offline access: **

SMS, Telecom USSD and SIM ToolKits, 

**2. Online access: **

* GynoSMART Bot on Telegram Messenger (download telegram messenger on IOS (Apple), Android (Google) and Windows App-stores, search for @gynosmart, click on start; 
* GynoSMART App (available in the Android/Google App-store, coming soon to other App-stores);
